HEADWORD: Tomnoddy
<hw>Tom"nod`dy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Tom</ets>
(see <er>Tomboy</er>) + <ets>noddy</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A sea bird, the puffin.</def>
